rComments: Doesn't let you be independent in assessment or baby baths, or even with another student. Limited learning, pre and post clinicals were not very pertinent, randomly anal about a few things but just say ok and do it.

She's great! As a clinical prof, very easy going, she's very easy, very very nice, can talk about anything with her. A little bit disorganized but no one is perfect. Could have been a little harder on us during clinicals but... not complaining.
